Woah-oh, woah-oh, woah-oh, woah-oh-oh-oh
Legendary
Woah-oh, woah-oh, woah-oh, woah-oh-oh-oh, yeah

Are you ready? Are you ready?

Woah-oh, woah-oh, woah-oh, woah-oh-oh-oh

Make way, make way
Woah-oh, woah-oh, woah-oh, woah-oh-oh-oh

Legendary

Just wait and see, wait and see, they gon' talk about me
Just wait and see, wait and see, they gon' talk about me
Just wait and see, wait and see, they gon' talk about me
